---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '21 February 2026';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — Property Web Scraper">

<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700">

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 text-sm text-amber-800">
      <strong>Important:</strong> These terms govern your use of PropertyWebScraper. By using this service you agree to them. If you do not agree, please do not use the service.
    </div>

    <!-- 1 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. No Affiliation with Property Portals</h2>
      <p>
        PropertyWebScraper is an independent tool. We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or partnered with
        Rightmove, Zillow, Idealista, Zoopla, Realtor.com, Domain.com.au, Funda, ImmoScout24, or any other property portal.
        All third-party brand names, trademarks, and logos belong to their respective owners.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 2 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Data Accuracy — Provided "As Is"</h2>
      <p>
        Extracted data is provided <strong>"as is"</strong> without warranty of any kind, express or implied.
        We make no representations about the completeness, accuracy, currency, or suitability of any extracted data.
        Property prices, availability, descriptions, and all other listing details are sourced from third-party websites
        and may be stale, incomplete, or mis-extracted. <strong>Always verify listing details directly with the source website or the listing agent</strong> before making any decisions.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We expressly disclaim all liability for any loss or damage arising from reliance on extracted data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 3 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Your Responsibility to Comply with Third-Party Terms</h2>
      <p>
        PropertyWebScraper processes HTML that <strong>you provide</strong>. We do not crawl or scrape websites on your behalf.
        You are solely responsible for ensuring that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
        <li>You have the right to access and process the HTML content you submit.</li>
        <li>Your use of this service complies with the Terms of Service, robots.txt directives, and any applicable usage policies of the website from which you obtained the HTML.</li>
        <li>You do not use this service to enable automated bulk collection that violates third-party terms or applicable law.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We reserve the right to suspend or terminate access for any user we reasonably believe is using the service in breach of third-party terms or applicable law.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 4 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Not Legal, Financial, or Investment Advice</h2>
      <p>
        Nothing produced by this service constitutes property valuation, investment advice, financial advice, legal advice,
        or any professional recommendation of any kind. Any price data, market information, or property details extracted
        through this service should not be used as the basis for investment or financial decisions without independent
        professional verification.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 5 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Responsible and Fair Use</h2>
      <p>
        This service is intended for personal research, business intelligence, and legitimate property market analysis.
        You agree not to use it to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
        <li>Build unauthorised competing products that re-publish third-party listing data.</li>
        <li>Circumvent technical protection measures on any website.</li>
        <li>Harvest, republish, or sell third-party listing data in a manner that violates applicable law or the source site's terms.</li>
        <li>Generate excessive automated load on any third-party website.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We enforce rate limits on all plans. Excessive or abusive usage may result in suspension without refund.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 6 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Personal Data in Extracted Content</h2>
      <p>
        Property listings sometimes contain personal data such as agent names, phone numbers, and email addresses.
        If you extract, store, or process such data, you are acting as a data controller (or equivalent under your local law)
        and are responsible for doing so in compliance with all applicable data protection legislation, including but not
        limited to the UK GDPR, EU GDPR, and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA).
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        PropertyWebScraper does not store submitted HTML beyond the time needed to process your request. Extracted
        structured data may be cached briefly to improve performance. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 7 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, PropertyWebScraper and its operators shall not be liable
        for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including loss of profits, data,
        or goodwill, arising from your use of — or inability to use — this service, even if we have been advised of
        the possibility of such damages.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Our total aggregate liability to you for any claim arising from use of the service shall not exceed the amount
        paid by you to us in the three months preceding the claim.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 8 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">8. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. Material changes will be notified by updating the "Last updated"
        date at the top of this page. Continued use of the service after any change constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 9 -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Email us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@propertywebscraper.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">hello@propertywebscraper.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
